data.description: 1318 S Elm is ready for its new owner! This adorable 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is located on a quiet cul-de-sac near downtown Henderson. Many updates completed recently throughout: HVAC (2020), Siding (2022), Roof (2022), Water Heater (2022), Gutters (2023), Warrantied Crawlspace (2023). The outside features include a large deck with a fenced in yard and a 16x24 foot storage building. Check it out today!
